data.name: Witchcrafter Haine
data.desc: Your opponent cannot target other Spellcaster monsters you control with card effects. (Quick Effect): You can discard 1 Spell, then target 1 face-up card your opponent controls; destroy it. You can only use this effect of "Witchcrafter Haine" once per turn.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
